    <p><strong>About Larsen &amp; Toubro (L&amp;T)</strong></p>
    <p><br /> Larsen &amp; Toubro (L&amp;T) is a globally recognized Indian multinational company with a rich legacy spanning over eight decades. Headquartered in Mumbai, L&amp;T operates in key sectors such as engineering, construction, technology, manufacturing, and financial services. Known for its commitment to excellence, innovation, and sustainability, L&amp;T plays a vital role in nation-building by executing some of the most complex and impactful infrastructure projects across India and in over 50 countries worldwide.</p>
    <p>The company is backed by a strong workforce, cutting-edge technologies, and a robust corporate governance structure. From large-scale transportation systems and smart cities to power plants, defense systems, and IT services, L&amp;T has built a reputation for delivering high-quality solutions that meet global standards.</p>
    <p><strong>L&amp;T Realty &ndash; Building the Future of Urban Living</strong></p>
    <p><br /> As a key vertical under the Larsen &amp; Toubro umbrella, <strong>L&amp;T Realty</strong> is the real estate development arm of the company. Since its inception, L&amp;T Realty has redefined the real estate landscape in India by creating residential, commercial, and retail spaces that blend quality, aesthetics, and functionality. With a strong presence in major cities such as Mumbai, Bengalore, Chennai, and Hyderabad, the division is known for its landmark developments and customer-centric approach.</p>
    <p>L&amp;T Realty is committed to delivering smart, sustainable spaces that reflect modern urban lifestyles. Its projects are characterized by thoughtful design, excellent construction quality, on-time delivery, and adherence to safety and environmental standards. Whether it&rsquo;s premium residential complexes, cutting-edge office spaces, or mixed-use developments, L&amp;T Realty continues to set new benchmarks in urban development and real estate innovation.</p>
